{{Quote|The Kingslayer, he escaped in the night!|The messenger to [[Robb Stark]]|The Prince of Winterfell}}
A '''Stark Messenger''' is an unnamed minor character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by guest star [[Moe Dunford]] and only appears in "[[The Prince of Winterfell]]."
sections.Biography:
===Background===
This soldier is a messenger for [[House Stark]].
===[[Season 2]]===
While [[Robb Stark|Robb]] and [[Talisa Stark|Talisa]] are walking back from [[The Crag]], he rides out to Robb, to announce that [[Jaime Lannister]] has escaped.<ref>"[[The Prince of Winterfell]]"</ref>
